Build a CRT Script for the following manual test case.

Steps:
1) Create a new Account record without selecting a region.
2) Save the record and verify that an error message is displayed, indicating that the region field is required.
3) Update the Account record by selecting a valid region.
4) Fill in a value for the phone number.
5) Make the Industry value "Banking".
6) Make the "Employees" field be 500.
7) Save the record and ensure that it is successfully saved without any errors.
8) Delete the Account record.
